description: Schedules a new run based on the request parameters and add it to the run queue.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group to which the container registry belongs.

registry_name.description: The name of the container registry.

run_request.description: The parameters of a run that needs to scheduled.

type.description: The type of the run request.

isarchiveenabled.description: The value that indicates whether archiving is enabled for the run or not.
